{
  "stem": "25598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just like to finish about my maternal grandmother with the fact-- and her family, the three sisters.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their family name was Siegler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want to talk a little bit about my father's parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandfather's name was Elchanan Steigman, and my grandmother's name was Beile Steigman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- we lived in the same house, which had the four apartments, and different apartments.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the relationship between them and my mother was not the best, which had an impact on me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I imagine that it was not the best, because my mother didn't bring the dowry that they expected.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nevertheless, we lived in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the backyard of the house, my grandparents had built a steady sukkah, which had a roof which opened up with a big stick.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was another very joyous holiday, because I loved to go and decorate the sukkah with my friends with leaves, and pine cones, and all kinds of fruit and stuff.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And sometimes, because we lived in the mountains, it was pretty cold to eat in the sukkah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But even if we had to wear sweaters, or even if we have to a winter coat, that was it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I would-- we would not eat anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was the sukkah for the whole week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's another very fond memory that, that I have from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Now, they had-- my paternal grandparents-- had three children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One, one's name was Rachel, and people say that I look like her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never met her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She died before I was born.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Another was Eti, and she was with us in the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She now lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And another is my father, who was the oldest, Elchanan Steigman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
